sources.title: MEAD | Full Movie | Action Sci-Fi Adventure | Exclusive!
sources.description:
MEAD - With plans of galaxy-wide domination, an evil Admiral creates MEAD, a powerful AI spaceship. But when MEAD becomes sentient and refuses to be used for war, he is to be decommissioned and escapes. Now, the fugitive starship and his Captain are chased across the solar system by bounty hunters and military forces, evading enemy advances with illusions so real that they fool their pursuers.
2022. Stars: Samuel Hunt, Robert Picardo, Patton Oswalt
